births-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>上汽IM Motors在欧洲启动2+级自动驾驶道路测试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/saics-im-motors-kicks-off-level-2-plus-autonomous-driving-road-testing-europe-2024-10-28/</link><description>据周一发布的一份公司声明称，中国国有上汽集团旗下的高端电动汽车品牌 IM Motors 已开始在欧洲市场进行 2 级以上自动驾驶道路测试。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 09:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/saics-im-motors-kicks-off-level-2-plus-autonomous-driving-road-testing-europe-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>无论选举如何，菲律宾对美国安全政策的连续性充满信心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-confident-us-security-policy-continuity-regardless-election-2024-10-28/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长吉尔伯托·特奥多罗表示，菲律宾对美国总统大选后美国在亚太地区政策的连续性充满信心，无论结果如何，两国关系都将保持牢固。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 07:38:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-confident-us-security-policy-continuity-regardless-election-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>飞利浦中国销量恶化导致股价暴跌16%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/philips-lowers-sales-outlook-china-demand-wanes-2024-10-28/</link><description>飞利浦周一表示，近几个月来中国的需求大幅下滑，迫使这家荷兰医疗设备制造商下调了今年的销售预期，导致其股价下跌 16%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 06:13:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/philips-lowers-sales-outlook-china-demand-wanes-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国再次警告欧盟不要与电动汽车制造商单独谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-again-warns-eu-against-separate-talks-with-ev-makers-2024-10-28/</link><description>中国商务部周一表示，中国再次向欧盟发出警告，如果欧盟在与中国谈判的同时与电动汽车公司单独进行谈判，将“动摇互信”并干扰整体谈判。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 06:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-again-warns-eu-against-separate-talks-with-ev-makers-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>一些公司在中国改变策略，看不到复苏的迹象</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/some-companies-change-tack-china-with-no-recovery-sight-2024-10-28/</link><description>由于房地产危机和失业率上升，客户正在削减支出。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 05:06:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/some-companies-change-tack-china-with-no-recovery-sight-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>上海警方出动警力制止喧闹的万圣节庆祝活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/police-out-force-prevent-rowdy-halloween-celebrations-shanghai-2024-10-28/</link><description>周末，上海警方在市中心街道巡逻，打击这座中国最国际化城市的万圣节庆祝活动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 03:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/police-out-force-prevent-rowdy-halloween-celebrations-shanghai-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国国债收益率上升，金价下跌，关注美国数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-slips-dollar-firms-market-eyes-crucial-us-data-2024-10-28/</link><description>由于美国国债收益率和美元走强，黄金创纪录的涨势在周一暂停，同时投资者等待本周公布的一系列美国经济数据，以获取有关美联储利率前景的线索。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 02:59:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-slips-dollar-firms-market-eyes-crucial-us-data-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国的私人辅导公司在镇压后走出阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-private-tutoring-firms-emerge-shadows-after-crackdown-2024-10-28/</link><description>目前还没有正式承认政策的变化。但现在政策制定者已经默许辅导行业的发展，北京方面的重点是支持创造就业机会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 02:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-private-tutoring-firms-emerge-shadows-after-crackdown-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国在年底贷款到期前推出新的贷款工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-activates-open-market-outright-reverse-repo-operations-2024-10-28/</link><description>中国央行周一推出了新的贷款工具，以在年底数万亿人民币贷款到期之前向市场注入更多流动性，并支持银行体系的信贷流动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 00:31:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-activates-open-market-outright-reverse-repo-operations-2024-10-28/</guid></item><item><title>据《华盛顿邮报》报道，中国黑客从未透露姓名的特朗普竞选顾问那里收集了音频</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/chinese-hackers-collected-audio-unnamed-trump-campaign-adviser-washington-post-2024-10-27/</link><description>据《华盛顿邮报》周日报道，中国政府相关黑客截获了美国政治人物的电话音频，其中包括共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普的一位未透露姓名的竞选顾问。</description><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/chinese-hackers-collected-audio-unnamed-trump-campaign-adviser-washington-post-2024-10-27/</guid></item><item><title>北京猛烈抨击美国军火交易后，台湾报告中国“战斗巡逻”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-countermeasures-after-2-bln-us-arms-sale-taiwan-2024-10-27/</link><description>美国批准了一项可能为台湾提供的价值 20 亿美元的一揽子计划，其中包括向台湾提供在乌克兰经过实战考验的先进防空导弹系统。</description><pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 00:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-countermeasures-after-2-bln-us-arms-sale-taiwan-2024-10-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>